lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps is going for his fifth — and he promises — last Olympics. Katie Ledecky is seeking to extend her dominance. Natalie Coughlin wants to end her career by making history. Ryan Lochte and Missy Franklin are back, too.

headline.main: Phelps Goes for 5th Olympics; Ledecky, Lochte in the Pool
